[p][img src="{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/9703436/d2ba186505121bbca2242bbbca398bf260a320cf.png"][/img][/p][p][i]by Eladrin[/i][/p][p][/p][p]Hi everyone![/p][p][/p][p]We've updated the [b]stellaris_test[/b] branch on Steam with a build that may fix some of the crashing issues that people are encountering, as well as a job assignment error that was breaking Virtuality and impacting Automatic Migration (and production in general).[/p][p][/p][p]This update is likely to go to the main live branches later on this week, probably Thursday.[/p][p][/p][p]To access this Open Beta branch until then, it’s available in Steam if you right click on Stellaris -> Properties -> Betas -> select "stellaris_test" branch in the Beta Participation dropdown. You may need to restart Steam to get it to appear.[/p]